<br/>
	Note: This sign is also good for keeping the
  vampires away. I haven't been bitten once. (That I know of.)</font></p>
<p>Note:  While I start with the right finger farther out than the left
  and then bring the right finger back (from "out to in") -- I've noticed that 
	<i>many</i> of my friends start with the right finger between their 
	chest and their left finger
  and then move their right finger forward until it touches the left finger.<br/>
